description.plain: Trinidad Cardona (b. May 23, 1999) is an R&B singer based in Phoenix, Arizona. He skyrocketed to Internet fame for his musical bathroom break hit titled “Jennifer”. He later released the Jennifer EP, including singles “Ready” and “You Are Mine”. Then, he released the albums Humble Beginnings, I Understand, Aventura and Por Favor.

songs.title: Jennifer

description.plain: This song is about how he messed up badly and had sex with Caroline, while he was “with” Jennifer. (Trinidad has said him and Jenny weren’t really dating.) He wrote this song as an apology to Jennifer for his mistake that caused them to break up, which maked him realize how much he really liked her.
